data.description: Welcome to this charming three-bedroom, two-full-bathroom brick-front townhouse in the heart of Constant Friendship, Abingdon. Step into a freshly rejuvenated space with brand-new carpet on the main and lower levels, creating a welcoming atmosphere throughout. The kitchen, adorned with an island, laminate flooring, and ample table space, is a perfect hub for both culinary endeavors and casual dining. The primary bedroom on the upper level boasts spaciousness and high ceilings, providing an airy retreat. The upper-level bathroom features a large soaking tub, perfect for unwinding after a long day. The fully finished lower level extends the living space, offering versatility and comfort. With a convenient walkout, it effortlessly connects indoor and outdoor living, leading to your backyard that backs to woods. This townhouse in Constant Friendship not only offers practical and modern features but also a tranquil environment. Perfectly situated in the sought-after community of Abingdon, this residence provides easy access to local amenities, parks, and more. Don't miss the chance to make this your new home! Schedule a showing today! Most recent updates: New carpet on main level and lower level, Nov. 2023. New HVAC and hot water heater, washer, dryer and dishwasher in 2021. Refrigerator, 2020.
